# NakedTransient/DecorateTransient
Widget 91
Property
    Position 30 80
    Type CheckBox
    Font -*-fixed-medium-r-semicondensed-*-13-*
    Flags NoReliefString Hidden   
    Title {                                                                               }
Main
 Case message of
  SingleClic :
  Begin
  End
End

